title: Week 2 Liquidity Mining Proposal
body:
This marks the second week of liquidity mining on Balancer v2. The Ballers propose allocating 2500 BAL to each of the following pools for the week starting Monday, May 31st at 00:00 UTC:

MKR/WETH 60/40
https://app.balancer.fi/#/pool/0xaac98ee71d4f8a156b6abaa6844cdb7789d086ce00020000000000000000001b

GTC/WETH 80/20
https://app.balancer.fi/#/pool/0xff083f57a556bfb3bbe46ea1b4fa154b2b1fbe88000200000000000000000030
